*guava-13.0.1-r1 (04 Sep 2015)

  04 Sep 2015; Patrice Clement <monsieurp@gentoo.org> +guava-13.0.1-r1.ebuild:
  Keyword for ppc+ppc64. Set a dependency on >=virtual/{jdk,jre}-1.6 in lieu
  of hard dependency on virtual/jdk:1.7 to allow for java-with-com-sun ebuild
  keywording.

  Package-Manager: portage-2.2.18
  Signed-off-by: Patrice Clement <monsieurp@gentoo.org>

*guava-13.0.1-r2 (10 Sep 2015)

  10 Sep 2015; Patrice Clement <monsieurp@gentoo.org> +guava-13.0.1-r2.ebuild:
